//i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBjwQ4y.jpg&h=fe3bb434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXcSp1djs5tejMpT4rA2daznAxLXwHuWwibkqxXjRD4sH?filename=i4t2dhT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi4t2dhT.jpg&h=096471d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPost by IG @girlsfoodies<br />\n<br />\n有傻賣了有傻賣了！<br />\n有大舖有細舖，大家幫襯邊間自己決定喇～<br />\n而家訂有好多舖仲有 Mee優惠喔～ @mee_punishc <br />\n<br />\n// 其實每次整呢啲表，都係希望大家唔好遺漏咗啲無咁出名嘅舖仔🥺<br />\n<br />\n有時某幾個品牌多人買到要打蛇餅拎貨，有啲品牌就囤哂貨😣 當然我唔能夠否定可能同品牌本身形象、口碑有關，難食嘅係抵佢被自然淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n但事實又唔係真係咁喎，有好多質素ok嘅小店，只係因為無人討論、無錢賣廣告而無人幫襯。我做到嘅嘢，就唯有係幫佢哋shout out，希望大家會forward畀其他朋友💛 //<br />\n<br />\n列表最後更新：2021/5/3 <br />\n#黃店 #端午節 #粽 #糭 #咸肉粽 #素粽 #素糭 #黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"487e2915e7a78913252b356151acbd02b08ca541","tid":2517694,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"圖口"},{"pid":"84bd1285f3933a0af326f1e78f0149e00f806a7f","tid":2517694,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c56729de1d3fb2eda85718d9dcc71c377bb43ee","tid":2517694,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c99338b6e5c23203311009ba5687a7d62190899","tid":2517694,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1aa5371e66a69e5ab04e45b8a7f03b8d40536f03","tid":2517694,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b406828ed5effbb38b20cb3c605c2e887d9fdf80","tid":2517694,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ccbaad0ee0c1db7946414890c6626219a0b305e","tid":2517694,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"push"